Claymore Silver ETF Discount at 3.8 Percent on Sept. 15

-- B y   M i k e   S e b a n y
-- 
2011-09-16T12:27:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/claymore-silver-etf-discount-at-3-8-percent-on-sept-15-table-.html
The Claymore Silver Bullion exchange-
traded fund closed at a discount of 3.79% on Sept. 15, according to
figures available on the fund’s website. A discount means that the
closing price of the shares is lower than the value of its underlying
holdings of the metal. The fund’s silver holdings were unchanged at 
1,186,000 ounces   
